SIMPLE: irrefragable
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irrefragable
<hw>Ir*ref"ra*ga*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>irr⟦eacute⟧fragable</ets>, L. <ets>irrefragabilis</ets>. See
<er>Refragable</er>.]</ety> <def>Not refragable; not to be gainsaid or
denied; not to be refuted or overthrown; irrefutable; unanswerable;
incontestable; undeniable; <as>as, an <ex>irrefragable</ex> argument;
<ex>irrefragable</ex> evidence.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ir*ref"ra*ga*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Ir*ref"ra*ga*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Incontrovertible; unanswerable; indisputable;
unquestionable; incontestable; indubitable; undeniable;
irrefutable.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irrefrangibility</ent>⟦br⟧
